abstract: >-
  A curated, opinionated map of self-evolving and self-improving LLM agents:
  automated agent/workflow design, test-time learning, evolving memory, skill
  acquisition, reinforcement learning for self-improvement, and the failure and
  safety problems these create — with two runnable reference implementations.
